snippet.title: Soul Searching Trailer
snippet.description:
Official site containing Purchase Options: http://playsoulsearching.com/
Available on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/586240

Soul Searching is a narrative survival game about sailing away from your homeland.
Soul Searching is a non-violent humble journey on primitive boats in a world of islands, dragons, and magic.
